{
  "page": "Invasion of the Arbor",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Invasion of the Arbor</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> and the surrounding islands, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a> victory\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ryamsport\" title=\"Ryamsport\">Ryamsport</a> is sacked</li>\n<li>The towns of <a href=\"/index.php/Vinetown\" title=\"Vinetown\">Vinetown</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Starfish_Harbor\" title=\"Starfish Harbor\">Starfish Harbor</a> on the Arbor and the islands of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonecrab_Cay\" title=\"Stonecrab Cay\">Stonecrab Cay</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Pigs\" title=\"Isle of Pigs\">Isle of Pigs</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid%27s_Palace\" title=\"Mermaid&#39;s Palace\">Mermaid's Palace</a> are occupied</li>\n<li>The islands of <a href=\"/index.php/Horseshoe_Rock\" title=\"Horseshoe Rock\">Horseshoe Rock</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard%27s_Cradle\" title=\"Bastard&#39;s Cradle\">Bastard's Cradle</a> are partially occupied</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6f/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"House Baratheon of King&#39;s Landing\">House Baratheon of King's Landing</a>:<br />\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tyrell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/45px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/60px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> The <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/20px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/30px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/40px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\">House Redwyne</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Greyjoy.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Greyjoy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/30px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/45px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/60px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">Kingdom of the Isles and the North</a></b>/ <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">12 war galleys<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Ironborn fleets, excluding the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">All ships captured or sunken<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>invasion of the Arbor</b> takes place in <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a> during the second phase of the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>, and is part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> campaign in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. Following the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>, the new <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">King of the Isles and the North</a>, sends his ships to raid up the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> as well as other parts of the Reach. With much of the Reach's armies and navies on campaign in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, the Reach is poorly defended.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Invasion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Invasion</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Invasion_of_the_Arbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Reports of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> taking the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_Islands\" title=\"Shield Islands\">Shield Islands</a> reach <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. The ironborn are said to have a thousand ships, although this is most likely an exaggeration. Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a> demands that the <a href=\"/index.php/Redwyne_fleet\" title=\"Redwyne fleet\">Redwyne fleet</a>, which is besieging <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(300)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (300)\">Storm’s End</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"Siege of Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, be allowed to leave the stormlands and the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> in order to defend the Reach, but Queen Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> refuses, stating that the two castles remain a danger to King's Landing and King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon's</a> rule as they remain loyal to a rival king, <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Margaery's brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a>, offers to lead a charge on the walls of Dragonstone in order to quickly end the siege, which Cersei accepts.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> A fortnight later it is reported that Loras has successfully taken the castle, being grievously wounded in the process, which allows for the Redwyne fleet to make for the Reach.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the meantime, <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> has ordered his fleet to carry out attacks on settlements of the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a>, and the Whispering Sound. King's Landing is informed of the presence of ironborn longships in the <a href=\"/index.php/Redwyne_Straits\" title=\"Redwyne Straits\">Redwyne Straits</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Invasion\">Invasion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Invasion_of_the_Arbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Invasion\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With most of the Redwyne fleet away, the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> capture or sink the dozen warships remaining at the Arbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The Arbor town of <a href=\"/index.php/Ryamsport\" title=\"Ryamsport\">Ryamsport</a> is sacked whilst <a href=\"/index.php/Vinetown\" title=\"Vinetown\">Vinetown</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Starfish_Harbor\" title=\"Starfish Harbor\">Starfish Harbor</a> are taken. The ironborn also capture the neighboring islands of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonecrab_Cay\" title=\"Stonecrab Cay\">Stonecrab Cay</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Pigs\" title=\"Isle of Pigs\">Isle of Pigs</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid%27s_Palace\" title=\"Mermaid&#39;s Palace\">Mermaid's Palace</a> whilst the islands of <a href=\"/index.php/Horseshoe_Rock\" title=\"Horseshoe Rock\">Horseshoe Rock</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard%27s_Cradle\" title=\"Bastard&#39;s Cradle\">Bastard's Cradle</a> are partially occupied.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Invasion_of_the_Arbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> learns about the Arbor's fate from the captain of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Huntress\" title=\"Huntress\">Huntress</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Invasion_of_the_Arbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>If <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> loses <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">whole realm</a> will fall to pieces, he thought as he watched the <a href=\"/index.php/Huntress\" title=\"Huntress\">Huntress</a> and her sisters moving off.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Invasion_of_the_Arbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-c